Paul Merson: &ldquo;The thing that surprises me with Arsenal is that you look at their team &amp; there aren&rsquo;t many that would get in all the other teams. They wouldn&rsquo;t get in anyone else&rsquo;s team in the top five. Nobody would take any of them.&rdquo; #afc<br />
<br />
Merson: &ldquo;The goalie, whole of the back four, Xhaka &amp; Elneny wouldn&rsquo;t get in. That is the worry. With Spurs, you could reel off a lot of players who, if they went up for sale tomorrow, big boys would snap them up. We point the finger at Ars&egrave;ne, but the players aren&rsquo;t good enough.&rdquo;
